ds/2023/10/porno-for-pyros@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/porno-for-pyros@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>佩里·法雷尔 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/perry-farrell">Perry Farrell</a> ) 领导的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/porno-for-pyros">Porno For Pyros</a>推迟了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/porno-for-pyros-announce-first-tour-in-25-years-to-celebrate-30th-anniversary-3467448">即将举行的巡演</a>，以完成新音乐的创作。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/perry-farrell-interview-porno-for-pyros-janes-addiction-new-music-eric-avery-billy-corgan-3302568">佩里·法雷尔 (Perry Farrell) 谈《Porno For Pyros》和《Jane&#39;s Addiction》的新音乐，以及埃里克·艾弗里 (Eric Avery) 的回归</a></strong></li></ul><p>乐队上周末在社交媒体上宣布了这一消息，并确认等待参加 Pyro For Pornos <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/porno-for-pyros-announce-first-tour-in-25-years-to-celebrate-30th-anniversary-3467448">25 年来首次巡演的</a>歌迷将不得不再等一段时间。乐队表示，推迟将让他们有时间完成巡演期间表演的新音乐。</p><p> “我们非常感谢你们过去 30 年来的所有支持，并渴望与你们一起庆祝。在为我们 25 年来的第一次巡演排练的同时，我们也在录音室创作新的音乐——我们希望能及时为您提供这些演出，”乐队写道。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CxyWvAsvA7V/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radiu